ActFood and Drugs Act
SubjectNatural Health Products (Unprocessed Product Licence Applications)Regulations
PrecisNATURAL HEALTH PRODUCTS (Unprocessed Product Licence Applications) REGULATIONS, in order to advance a temporary instrument for natural health products that have a product licence application awaiting review by Health Canada by expressly exempting them from the prohibition against sale in the Natural Health Products Regulations. The Regulations introduce a more appropriate level of safety oversight to these products.
